Fred the Feedback Channel

About a year ago I had the course User Interface Design. It was the first UX course with real hands-on project and finally it gave my studies a new direction!

In the UID course we made the group project in which we designed and prototyped an application that helps citizens to give feedpack on public transportation. This was a new kind of task for me and a lot of things in the user study and the design process we did with my group in the exercisess since it was the first time we heard of UI design and things to consider. My personal resposibility in that project was to make the sketches of the mobile application. I tried making them in the app InVision and since then it has been a regular tool for me.
